  "texts": [
    "This decorrelated input is then used as input for the layer's non-linear transformation",
    "which may be either the kernel function of a convolutional layer applied to a (flattened) input patch or the transformation in a fully-connected layer.",
    "Since the application of the decorrelation matrix R on the correlated input x is a linear transformation, the full layer transformation can also be described as",
    "(3) with A = WR.",
    "The output of the layer then becomes the correlated input to the next layer."
